<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>User connected list</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/insights/v3.0/resource/query/mobileusers/gp/noc_current_connected_user_list"}></MethodEndpoint>



Retrieves a list of all users currently active on the GlobalProtect Gateway.
If a DEM or ADEM license is present, the time range filter is used to compute the experience score.
